name: com.castsoftware.jaxws
title: JAX-WS Analyzer
description: This extension provides support of JAX-WS Web Services used in JEE applications. It's handle a collection of annotations introduced with(JSR 224)enabling the definition of SOAP web services contract directly inside the java code.This extension detects also Webservice implemention when Apache CXF/Spring framework is used (through XML configuration files)and Client-side WebServices created via Spring WebServiceTemplate
